quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,73,"Men waЙ—i Й“e AlmaamiiЙ“e hiЙ“e fewna e Yamiroore Amen Men Wahayini faade e maЙ“Й“e gollugol moЖҙЖҙi Й—in e Гұinnugol Julde nden e Okkugol Jakka on, Й“e laatinoke ko Й“e Reway Й“e Men"
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo Г‘eeГұal e Ganndal, Men danndi mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yimЙ“e mu'un] laatinoo no golla soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke yimЙ“e bonЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,76,"E Nuuhu tuma nde o noddunoo ko adii, Men jaabinani mo kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden immorde e saЙ—teende mawnde nden"
  21,77,"Men walli mo immorde e Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatino yimЙ“e bonЙ“e, Men yooli Й“e, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  21,78,E Daawuuda e Sulaymaana tuma nde Й“e Гұaawaynoo fii ngesa mban tuma nde bonnunoo e nder mabba dammi yimЙ“e Й“en Men woni seediiЙ“e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden
  21,79,"Men Faamini nde Sulaymaana [Гұaawoore nden] gooto-kala e maЙ“Й“e Men Okki Г‘eeГұel e Ganndal Men elti wonndude e Daawuuda pelle Й—en hiЙ—e subhinoo e colli Й—in kadi, Men laatike golluЙ“e"
  21,80,"Men Anndini [Daawuuda] moЖҙЖҙinngol mekeГұaaji fii mo'on, fii yo Й—i reenu on immorde e hare mo'on. Taw si onon ko on jarnooЙ“e"
  21,81,"[Men eltani] Sulaymaana henndu ndun ko ndu bippooru hindu doga e yamiroore makko, faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barki e mu'un. Men laatike AnnduЙ“e kala huunde"
